description: Feature Description : Verifying Login functionality for ITOpsAdmin
name: Login with ITOpsAdmin

elements.name: Successful Login with ITOpsAdmin

steps.name: User with ITOps role renders the URL
user enters Username as "Itops_admin", Password as "qa123" and clicks on Login button
ITOps home page is displayed

elements.name: Verifying Admin is able to Configure New Severity Mapping

steps.name: "Admin" navigates to ust home page
"Admin" enters project name as "Automation_IB_16" in the search field
"Admin" clicks on project name "Automation_IB_16"
"Admin" clicks on Configuration tab
"Admin" clicks on Severity Mapping
"Admin" clicks on Add new source button
"Admin" clicks on source dropdown and select a source
"Admin" enters source Severity as "2323"
"Admin" clicks on SO Severity dropdown and selects Information
"Admin" clicks on + button
"Admin" enters next source Severity as "324"
"Admin" clicks on next SO Severity dropdown and selects Information
"Admin" clicks on Add Source button
Success message for Severity Mapping must be shown in popup "Severity mapping details are successfully Inserted"

elements.name: Verifying Admin is able to Configure New Severity Mapping

steps.name: "Admin" clicks on Severity Mapping
"Admin" verifies Source Severity text feild as "SOURCE SEVERITY"
"Admin" verifies SO Severity as "SO SEVERITY"
"Admin" verifies Updated time as "UPDATED TIME"
"Admin" verifies +Add Severity as "Add Severity"
"Admin" verifies Delete icon
"Admin" verifies Add New Source as "Add New Source"
"Admin" verifies Edit icon
"Admin" verifies Delete icon of specefic Severity

elements.name: Verifying Admin is able to Configure New Severity Mapping

steps.name: "Admin" clicks on Severity Mapping
"Admin" clicks on Add new source button
"Admin" clicks on source dropdown and select a source
"Admin" enters source Severity as "23"
"Admin" clicks on SO Severity dropdown and selects Information
"Admin" clicks on Add Source button
Error message for creating duplicate source must be shown in popup "Source already exists"

elements.name: Adding additional source severity within the another source

steps.name: "Admin" clicks on Severity Mapping
'Admin' clicks on cancel button
'Admin' clicks on Add new source button
'Admin' clicks on source dropdown and select a source
'Admin' enters source Severity as "2623"
'Admin' clicks on SO Severity dropdown and selects Information
'Admin' clicks on Add Source button
Success message for Verifyimg adding additional source severity within the another source must be shown in popup "Source already exists"

elements.name: Verify adding additional source severity within the same source

steps.name: "Admin" clicks on Severity Mapping
'Admin' clicks on cancel button
"Admin" clicks on + Add Severity button
"Admin" enters source Severity as "264"
"Admin" clicks on SO Severity dropdown and selects Information
"Admin" clicks on save and add new button
"Admin" enters source Severity as "3773"
"Admin" clicks on SO Severity dropdown and selects Information
"Admin" click on save button
Success message for Verifyimg adding additional source severity within the same source must be shown in popup "New severity mapping successfully added"

elements.name: Verifying that Admin is able to create duplicate source severity and SO severity

steps.name: "Admin" clicks on Severity Mapping
'Admin' clicks on edit button
'Admin' changes source Severity as "264"
'Admin' clicks on save button
'Admin' clicks on yes button
Error message for creating duplicate source severity must be shown in popup "Severity mapping for Source Severity already exists"
'Admin' clicks on edit button
'Admin' changes another source Severity as "32"
'Admin' clicks on save button
'Admin' clicks on yes button
Success message for updating Severity Mapping must be shown in popup "Successfully Updated."

description: Feature Description : Verifying Display Configuration functionalities
name: Display Configuration

elements.name: Verify whether itops_admin is able to view Display Configuration settings

steps.name: "Admin" clicks on Alert Console Display Configuration from LHS menu Settings
"Admin" verifies that Primary and secondary sections are present
"Admin" verifies Up and Down arrows are present in both sections
"Admin" verifies left and right arrows are present

elements.name: Default buttons in Display Configuration page

steps.name: "Admin" verifies Save configuration and cancel buttons are present
"Admin" verifies Save configuration button disabled by default

elements.name: Verify the default fields in Primary section

steps.name: "Admin" verifies all the primary section fields are present
"Admin" clicks on "alertID" from primary section
"Admin" clicks on Right Arrow key to move the field to secondary section
"Admin" verifies "alertID" is not moved to secondary section

elements.name: Verify user is able to change display name of Primary fields

steps.name: "Admin" clicks on a field name and edits the name as "Test" in primary section
"Admin" clicks on Save configuration button
"Admin" verifies if "Alert Console Settings saved Successfully" message is displayed

elements.name: Verify user is able to change display name of Secondary  fields

steps.name: "Admin" clicks on a field name and edits the name as "Value" in secondary section
"Admin" clicks on Save configuration button
"Admin" verifies if "Alert Console Settings saved Successfully" message is displayed

elements.name: ReOrdering of Primary section fields

steps.name: "Admin" selects a "nodeName" and clicks on Up arrow to reOrder
"Admin" clicks on Save configuration button
"Admin" verifies if "Alert Console Settings saved Successfully" message is displayed
"Admin" verifies "6" of the "nodeName" is as per the new order
"Admin" selects a "nodeName" and clicks on down arrow to reOrder
"Admin" clicks on Save configuration button
"Admin" verifies if "Alert Console Settings saved Successfully" message is displayed
"Admin" verifies "7" of the "nodeName" is as per the new order

elements.name: Active and Inactive fields in secondary section

steps.name: "Itops_Engineer" navigate to Configuration section
"Admin" clicks on Alert Console Display Configuration from LHS menu Settings
"Admin" selects "objectStatus" and clicks on toggle bar to inactive the field in Secondary section
"Admin" clicks on Save configuration button
"Admin" verifies if "Alert Console Settings saved Successfully" message is displayed

elements.name: Maximum fields in Primary section

steps.name: "Itops_Engineer" navigate to Configuration section
"Admin" clicks on Alert Console Display Configuration from LHS menu Settings
"Admin" selects "resourceGroup", "connectedTo", "region", "site", "portNumber" and "resourceType" from Secondary to Primary section
if number of fields are more than 16, "The maximum number of columns that can be added as primary column is 16" message should be displayed

elements.name: Verify user is able to interchange primary fields and secondary fields

steps.name: "Itops_Engineer" navigate to Configuration section
"Admin" clicks on Alert Console Display Configuration from LHS menu Settings
"Admin" selects "alertMessage" in the primary section and clicks on Left arrow button
"Admin" clicks on Save configuration button
"Admin" verifies if "Alert Console Settings saved Successfully" message is displayed
